# Cursor Rules

## Git Workflow
- NEVER skip the ChatGPT review process (git commit --no-verify)
- Always wait for the ChatGPT review to complete before proceeding with commits
- If the review fails, address the issues raised before committing

## Code Quality
- Follow the project's coding standards
- Ensure all tests pass before committing
- Document any significant changes

## Security
- Never commit sensitive information
- Follow security best practices
- Review all environment variables and secrets 